                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8888" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2227</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">815 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不走寻常路，区域隐形冠军南城香的成长之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Forging an Unconventional Path: The Regional “Hidden Champion” Growth Path of Nancheng Xiang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关鑫，郑文丽，吴心月，杨大龙，张瑛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">首都经济贸易大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京南城香餐饮有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隐形冠军；南城香；成长战略；创新能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Hidden Champion; Nancheng Xiang; Growth Strategy; Innovation Ability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了餐饮连锁企业南城香从一个快餐小店，经过20多年的发展，成为一个年营业收入超10亿元、直营门店超180家的区域隐形冠军。从“踩坑无数，摸爬滚打15年找到方向”到“向死而生，‘异类’南城香模式落地成型”，再到“步步为营，在机遇与升级中实现创新突破”，南城香不断调整战略，扎根社区，精准定位，在一步步变革与完善中实现隐形冠军梦。变革组织架构、树立经营理念、调整经营模式、增加营收渠道，每一步变革，南城香都在开辟特立独行的新路径；数字选址、团餐定制、三元自助、蔬菜种植，每一次完善，南城香都在向着百年品牌的目标迈进。通过对本案例的学习，可以帮助学生了解隐形冠军的概念和特点，指导学生结合战略选择理论、核心竞争力、数字化赋能等相关知识点，探讨并分析中国餐饮企业如何培养和发展创新能力，以及企业应采取何种战略，以适应快速变化的市场环境。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes how the catering chain enterprise Nancheng Xiang has evolved from a fast food small restaurant to a regional hidden champion with an annual revenue of over 1 billion yuan and over 180 directly operated stores, after more than 20 years of development. From stepping on countless pitfalls, struggling for 15 years to find direction to born from death, the &#39;exotic&#39; Nancheng Xiang incense model has taken shape. Then step by step, it achieves innovative breakthroughs in opportunities and upgrades. Nancheng Xiang continuously adjusts its strategy, takes root in the community, accurately positions itself, and realizes its hidden champion dream through step-by-step transformation and improvement. Each step of change, such as reshaping organizational structure, establishing business philosophy, adjusting business models, and increasing revenue channels, indicates that Nancheng Xiang is opening up a new path of independence and innovation. Digital site selection, group meal production, three yuan self-service, vegetable planting, every improvement suggests that Nancheng Xiang is moving towards the goal of becoming a century old brand. Through the study of this case, students can better understand the concept and characteristics of hidden champion enterprise. Meanwhile, they can combine strategic choice theory, core competitiveness, digital empowerment and other related knowledge points to analyse how Chinese restaurant enterprises cultivate and develop innovative capabilities and what strategies the enterprise should adopt to adapt to rapidly changing market environments.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略选择；核心竞争力；战略逻辑；差异化战略；创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
